    "This highlights the importance of precise and accurate prompting in achieving reliable diagnostic results.",
    "Factors like age, race, and ethnicity were excluded in the prompt.",
    "For the classification of hyperplastic polyps (HP), sessile serrated adenomas (SSA), and tubular adenomas (TA), each image was uploaded with the prompt: \"What polyp is this?",
    "Sessile serrated adenoma (SSA) or tubular adenoma or Hyperplastic polyps?",
    "Just give me the conclusion, no description is needed.\""
  ]
